{
  "chapter": 112,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕轩辕三光（外号\"恶赌鬼\"）在赌场大杀四方展开。他与黑瘦汉子合伙开赌，屠娇娇和白开心在旁观战，黑瘦汉子施展古怪轻功从人群中揪出赖账者。三位容貌一模一样的少妇突然到来，为首的紫衣少妇豪掷五万两白银连押六次\"双\"，骰子却开出六次\"单\"，二十万两白银输光后面不改色从容离去。轩辕三光被其豪赌气度折服，破例允许赊账继续，紫衣少妇最终答应再赌。本章生动刻画了轩辕三光的豪迈赌技与紫衣少妇三姊妹的神秘镇定，为后续剧情埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人群中",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七点，是单，我赢了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有赢家就有输家，入你先人板板，输钱的龟儿子先来磕头吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "格老子，五十个，你龟儿子居然想赢老子们五十两银子……是哪一个，快出来磕头。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_pi_gao_yao_han",
      "speaker_name": "贴膏药汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是我押的……不是我押的……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人不但轻功高明，而且身法古怪得很，我简直连见都没见过。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们好像见过，只不过……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过现在已经忘记了，是么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gou_pi_gao_yao_han",
      "speaker_name": "贴膏药汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是我，你看错了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "格老子，你龟儿子以为老子们的眼睛不管用么，你龟儿子不妨问问这里的人，老子们几时看错过。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赌奸赌猾不赌赖，你龟儿连这规矩都不懂，还敢来赌钱……快滚你妈的臭蛋吧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看这'恶赌鬼'现在已经该改个外号了。奇怪的是，这黑小子怎会也跟着他一起发疯呢？难道他们这些银子是从天上掉下来的么？她笑了笑，又接道：这也许是因为这小子太年轻，还不懂得银钱的可爱，等他到了我这样的年纪，他就会知道世上再也没有比银钱更可爱的东西了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龟儿子们，都押好了么？老子又要开了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢，等我一等。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赌场里的规矩，你既然来迟了，就得押下一把，但看在你说话的声音很好听的份上，就等你一等。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han_leader",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闪开，让条路出来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到我们这小庙里竟来了大菩萨。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_hei_shou_han_zi",
      "text": "兄弟，你不是总说赌得不过瘾么？看样子过瘾的已经来了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "有劳久候，抱歉得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "没得关系，我已有很久没有跟美人赌钱了，再等等都没得关系。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "好，现在姑娘们已经可以下注了，请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "原来姑娘们竟真的是准备来好好赌一场的，姑娘们找到了我，实在真是找对了人了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这里限不限注的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "你只管放心，随便你押多少，庄家都照赔不误。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这样最好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "五万，双！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "你看这三个美人儿真是来赌钱的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "像她们这样的人，就算要赌钱，也不会巴巴的赶到这里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "那么，她们难道是想来找这赌鬼麻烦的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "我现在也还看不透她们的用意，反正你等着瞧吧！这'恶赌鬼'今天绝不会有好日子过的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，要得，硬是要得，硬是过瘾。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五点，单，庄家赢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "五万，还是双。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "对，有赌不为输，再来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han_leader",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "还有二十万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这次全押上吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "双！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "这次你真的还是押双么？好，要得，连老子都服你了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "姑娘们且慢走。像姑娘们这样的赌客，虽非千载难逢，也是天下少有的。一个赌鬼遇见姑娘这样的对手，若是轻轻放过了，这赌鬼就该打下十八层地狱。姑娘们难道不想翻本？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "只可惜我们今天已输光了，过两天吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "赌场本来讲究的是现赌现赔，绝不赊欠，但对姑娘们这样的赌客，却可以例外。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "姑娘们尽管押吧，无论要押多少，只要一句话就算数。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少妇",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你信得过我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_fu",
      "text": "只要姑娘肯赌，我还怕姑娘会少了我一两银子么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道这恶赌鬼不肯放她们走的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 112,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    }
  ],
